{"id":161,"parent_id":158,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":161,"title":"2 Corinthians 3","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Cor.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 3"],[".studySummary",["i","The gospel surpasses the law of Moses—Where the Spirit of the Lord is, there is liberty."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.1","order":"03.10.003.18531"},["b","1"],"Do we begin again to commend ourselves? or need we, as some",["i","others,"],"epistles of commendation to you, or",["i","letters"],"of commendation from you?"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.2","order":"03.10.003.18532"},["b","2"],"Ye are our",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"epistle"],"written in our hearts, known and read of all men:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.3","order":"03.10.003.18533"},["b","3"],["i","Forasmuch as ye are"],"manifestly declared to be the epistle of Christ ministered by us,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"written"],"not with ink, but with the Spirit of the living God; not in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"tables"],"of stone, but in",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"fleshy"],"tables of the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_3d"},"heart"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.4","order":"03.10.003.18534"},["b","4"],"And such trust have we through Christ to God-ward:"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.5","order":"03.10.003.18535"},["b","5"],"Not that we are sufficient of ourselves to think any thing as of ourselves; but our",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"sufficiency"],["i","is"],"of God;"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.6","order":"03.10.003.18536"},["b","6"],"Who also hath made us able",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"ministers"],"of the new testament; not of the letter, but of the spirit: for the letter killeth, but the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"spirit"],"giveth life."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.7","order":"03.10.003.18537"},["b","7"],"But if the ministration of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"death"],", written",["i","and"],"engraven in stones, was glorious, so that the children of Israel could not steadfastly behold the face of Moses for the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"glory"],"of his countenance; which",["i","glory"],"was to be done away:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.8","order":"03.10.003.18538"},["b","8"],"How shall not the ministration of the spirit be rather glorious?"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.9","order":"03.10.003.18539"},["b","9"],"For if the ministration of condemnation",["i","be"],"glory, much more doth the ministration of righteousness exceed in glory."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.10","order":"03.10.003.18540"},["b","10"],"For even that which was made glorious had no glory in this respect, by reason of the glory that excelleth."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.11","order":"03.10.003.18541"},["b","11"],"For if that which is done away",["i","was"],"glorious, much more that which remaineth",["i","is"],"glorious."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.12","order":"03.10.003.18542"},["b","12"],"Seeing then that we have such hope, we use great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"plainness"],"of speech:"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.13","order":"03.10.003.18543"},["b","13"],"And not as Moses,",["i","which"],"put a veil over his face, that the children of Israel could not steadfastly look to the end of that which is abolished:"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.14","order":"03.10.003.18544"},["b","14"],"But their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"minds"],"were",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"blinded"],": for until this day remaineth the same veil untaken away in the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"reading"],"of the old testament; which",["i",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_14d"},"veil"]],"is done away in Christ."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.15","order":"03.10.003.18545"},["b","15"],"But even unto this day, when Moses is read, the veil is upon their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"heart"],"."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.16","order":"03.10.003.18546"},["b","16"],"Nevertheless when it shall turn to the Lord, the veil shall be taken away."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.17","order":"03.10.003.18547"},["b","17"],"Now the Lord is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"that Spirit"],": and where the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"Spirit"],"of the Lord",["i","is,"],"there",["i","is"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"liberty"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.18","order":"03.10.003.18548"},["b","18"],"But we all, with open face beholding as in a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"glass"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"glory"],"of the Lord, are changed into the same",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"image"],"from",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_18d"},"glory"],"to glory,",["i","even"],"as by the Spirit of the Lord."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.2a","order":"03.10.003.18549"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.2"},"1 Cor. 9:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.3a","order":"03.10.003.18551"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/9.10.10-11"},"Deut. 9:10 (10–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.3b","order":"03.10.003.18553"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/24.12"},"Ex. 24:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/31.18"},"31:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/34.1"},"34:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.13"},"Deut. 4:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/3.3"},"Prov. 3:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.3c","order":"03.10.003.18555"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/11.19.19-20"},"Ezek. 11:19 (19–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.3d","order":"03.10.003.18557"},["b","3d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/31.33"},"Jer. 31:33"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.10"},"Heb. 8:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.5a","order":"03.10.003.18559"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.16"},"2 Cor. 2:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/26.12"},"Alma 26:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.6a","order":"03.10.003.18561"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.5"},"1 Cor. 3:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.6b","order":"03.10.003.18563"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/6.63"},"John 6:63"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.7a","order":"03.10.003.18565"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.10"},"Rom. 7:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.7b","order":"03.10.003.18567"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/transfiguration"},"TG Transfiguration"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.12a","order":"03.10.003.18569"},["b","12a"],["span.small","GR"],"boldness, frankness."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.14a","order":"03.10.003.18571"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mind"},"TG Mind"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.14b","order":"03.10.003.18573"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spiritual-blindness"},"TG Spiritual Blindness"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.14c","order":"03.10.003.18575"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.21"},"Acts 15:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"14d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.14d","order":"03.10.003.18577"},["b","14d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-anticipation"},"TG Jesus Christ, Types of, in Anticipation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/veil"},"Veil"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.15a","order":"03.10.003.18579"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hardheartedness"},"TG Hardheartedness"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.17a","order":"03.10.003.18581"},["b","17a"],["span.small","GR"],"the Spirit."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.17b","order":"03.10.003.18583"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/61.15"},"Alma 61:15"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-spirit-of"},"TG God, Spirit of"],"."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.17c","order":"03.10.003.18585"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/8.2"},"Rom. 8:2"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/governments"},"TG Governments"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/liberty"},"Liberty"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.18a","order":"03.10.003.18587"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.12"},"1 Cor. 13:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.18b","order":"03.10.003.18589"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/celestial-glory"},"TG Celestial Glory"],"."],["div",{"id":"18c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.18c","order":"03.10.003.18591"},["b","18c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/8.29"},"Rom. 8:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"18d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.18d","order":"03.10.003.18593"},["b","18d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-potential-to-become-like-heavenly-father"},"TG Man, Potential to Become like Heavenly Father"],"."]]}
